#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:487
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Test File`: Enable this option to test the FEC file generation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Testitiedosto`: Ota tämä asetus käyttöön testataksesi FEC-"
"tiedoston luontia."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:488
msgid ":guilabel:`Excluded Journals`"
