msgstr ""
"**EDI**: Electronic Data Interchange, joka tässä viittaa sähköiseen laskuun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:149
msgid ""
"**SUNAT**: is the organization that enforces customs and taxation in Peru."
msgstr "**SUNAT**: organisaatio, joka valvoo tulli- ja verotusta Perussa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:150
msgid ""
"**OSE**: Electronic Service Operator, `OSE SUNAT's definition <https://"
