#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/asiapay.rst:0
msgid ""
"By default, the payment provider AsiaPay is configured to verify the secret "
"hash with the hash function `SHA1`. If a different function is :ref:`set on "
"your account <payment_providers/asiapay/configure_dashboard>`, activate "
"the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` and set the same value to the "
"field :guilabel:`Secure Hash Function` in the :guilabel:`Credentials` tab."
msgstr ""
"Oletuksena maksuntarjoaja AsiaPay on määritetty tarkistamaan salainen hash-"
"arvo hash-funktiolla `SHA1`. Jos tilillesi on :ref:`määritetty eri funktio "
"<payment_providers/asiapay/configure_dashboard>`, "
"aktivoi :ref:`kehittäjätila <developer-mode>` ja aseta sama arvo "
"kenttään :guilabel:`Secure Hash Function` :guilabel:`Tunnistetiedot`-"
"välilehdellä."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:3
msgid "Authorize.Net"
msgstr "Authorize.Net"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Authorize.Net <https://www.authorize.net>`_ is a United States-based online "
"payment solution provider, allowing businesses to accept **credit cards**."
msgstr ""
"`Authorize.Net <https://www.authorize.net>`_ on yhdysvaltalainen online-"
"maksuratkaisujen tarjoaja, jonka avulla yritykset voivat hyväksyä "
"**luottokorttimaksuja**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:17
msgid ""
"Odoo needs your **API Credentials & Keys** to connect with your "
"Authorize.Net account, which comprise:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo tarvitsee **API-tunnistetietosi ja -avaimesi** yhteyden muodostamiseksi "
"Authorize.Net-tilillesi. Niihin kuuluvat:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:20
msgid ""
"**API Login ID**: The ID solely used to identify the account with "
"Authorize.Net."
msgstr ""
"**API Login ID**: Yksinomaan tiliin tunnistamiseen Authorize.Netin kanssa "
"käytettävä tunnus."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:21
msgid "**API Transaction Key**"
msgstr "**API Transaction Key**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:22
msgid "**API Signature Key**"
msgstr "**API Signature Key**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:23
msgid "**API Client Key**"
msgstr "**API Client Key**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:25
msgid ""
"To retrieve them, log into your Authorize.Net account, go "
"to :menuselection:`Account --> Settings --> Security Settings --> API "
"Credentials & Keys`, generate your **Transaction Key** and **Signature "
"Key**, and paste them on the related fields in Odoo. Then, click on "
"**Generate Client Key**."
msgstr ""
"Hae ne kirjautumalla Authorize.Net-tilillesi, siirry "
"kohtaan :menuselection:`Account --> Settings --> Security Settings --> API "
"Credentials & Keys`, luo **Transaction Key** ja **Signature Key** ja liitä "
"ne Odon vastaaviin kenttiin. Napsauta sitten **Generate Client Key**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:31
msgid ""
"To test Authorize.Net with a *sandbox* account, change the :guilabel:`State` "
"to :guilabel:`Test Mode`. We recommend doing this on a test Odoo database, "
"rather than on your main database."
msgstr ""
"Testaa Authorize.Net *sandbox*-tilillä vaihtamalla :guilabel:`Tila` "
"arvoon :guilabel:`Testitila`. Suosittelemme tekemään tämän Odon "
"testitietokannassa päätietokannan sijaan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:34
msgid ""
"If you use the :guilabel:`Test Mode` with a regular account, it results in "
"the following error: *The merchant login ID or password is invalid or the "
"account is inactive*."
msgstr ""
"Jos käytät :guilabel:`Testitilaa` tavallisella tilillä, tuloksena on "
"seuraava virhe: *The merchant login ID or password is invalid or the account "
"is inactive*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:38
msgid "Configuration tab"
msgstr "Määritys-välilehti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:41
msgid "Place a hold on a card"
msgstr "Aseta pidätys kortille"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:43
msgid ""
"With Authorize.Net, you can enable the :ref:`manual capture "
"<payment_providers/manual_capture>`. If enabled, the funds are reserved for "
"30 days on the customer's card, but not charged yet."
msgstr ""
"Authorize.Netin kanssa voit ottaa käyttöön :ref:`manuaalisen veloituksen "
"<payment_providers/manual_capture>`. Jos se on käytössä, varat varataan 30 "
"päiväksi asiakkaan kortilta, mutta niitä ei veloiteta vielä."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:48
msgid ""
"After **30 days**, the transaction is **voided automatically** by "
"Authorize.Net."
msgstr ""
"**30 päivän** kuluttua Authorize.Net **mitätöi tapahtuman automaattisesti**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:56
msgid "ACH payments (USA only)"
msgstr "ACH-maksut (vain Yhdysvallat)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:58
msgid ""
":abbr:`ACH (automated clearing house)` is an electronic funds transfer "
"system used between bank accounts in the United States."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`ACH (automated clearing house)` on Yhdysvalloissa pankkitilien "
"välillä käytettävä sähköinen varojen siirtojärjestelmä."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:64
msgid ""
"To give customers the possibility to pay using ACH, `sign up for "
"Authorize.Net eCheck's service <https://www.authorize.net/payments/"
"echeck.html>`_. Once eCheck is activated, duplicate the previously "
"configured Authorize.Net payment provider on Odoo by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Payment Providers --> "
"Authorize.net`. Then, click the cog icon (:guilabel:`⛭`) and "
"select :guilabel:`Duplicate`. Change the provider's name to differentiate "
"both versions (e.g., `Authorize.net - Banks`)."
msgstr ""
"Jotta asiakkaat voivat maksaa ACH:lla, `rekisteröidy Authorize.Netin eCheck-"
"palveluun <https://www.authorize.net/payments/echeck.html>`_. Kun eCheck on "
"aktivoitu, monista aiemmin määritetty Authorize.Net-maksuntarjoaja Odossa "
"siirtymällä kohtaan :menuselection:`Kirjanpito --> Määritys --> "
"Maksuntarjoajat --> Authorize.net`. Napsauta sitten hammaspyöräkuvaketta "
"(:guilabel:`⚙`) ja valitse :guilabel:`Monista`. Vaihda tarjoajan nimi "
"erottaaksesi molemmat versiot (esim. `Authorize.net - Pankit`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:71
msgid ""
"When ready, change the provider's :guilabel:`State` to :guilabel:`Enabled` "
"for a regular account or :guilabel:`Test Mode` for a sandbox account."
msgstr ""
"Kun olet valmis, vaihda palveluntarjoajan :guilabel:`tila` "
"arvoon :guilabel:`Käytössä` tavallista tiliä varten "
"tai :guilabel:`testitila` sandbox-tiliä varten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:75
msgid "Import an Authorize.Net statement"
msgstr "Authorize.Net-tiliotteen tuonti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:80
msgid "Export from Authorize.Net"
msgstr "Vienti Authorize.Net-järjestelmästä"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:84
msgid ""
":download:`Download the Excel import template. <authorize/authorize-net-"
"magic-sheet.xlsx>`"
msgstr ""
":download:`Lataa Excel-tuontipohja. <authorize/authorize-net-magic-"
"sheet.xlsx>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:86
msgid "Log in to Authorize.Net."
msgstr "Kirjaudu sisään Authorize.Net-järjestelmään."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:87
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Account --> Statements --> eCheck.Net Settlement "
"Statement`."
msgstr ""
"Siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`Account --> Statements --> eCheck.Net "
"Settlement Statement`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:88
msgid ""
"Define an export range using an *opening* and *closing* batch settlement. "
"All transactions within the two batch settlements will be exported to Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Määritä vientialue käyttämällä *avaavaa* ja *sulkevaa* eräselvitystä. Kaikki "
"näiden kahden eräselvityksen välissä olevat tapahtumat viedään Odoohon."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:90
msgid ""
"Select all transactions within the desired range, copy them, and paste them "
"into the :guilabel:`Report 1 Download` sheet of the :ref:`Excel import "
"template <authorize-import-template>`."
msgstr ""
"Valitse kaikki halutun alueen tapahtumat, kopioi ne ja liitä "
"ne :guilabel:`Report 1 Download` -välilehteen :ref:`Excel-tuontipohjassa "
"<authorize-import-template>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:None
msgid "Selecting Authorize.Net transactions to import"
msgstr "Authorize.Net-tapahtumien valinta tuontia varten"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:None
msgid "Settlement batch of an Authorize.Net statement"
msgstr "Authorize.Net-tiliotteen selvityserä"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:103
msgid ""
"In this case, the first batch (01/01/2021) of the year belongs to the "
"settlement of 12/31/2020, so the **opening** settlement is from 12/31/2020."
msgstr ""
"Tässä tapauksessa vuoden ensimmäinen erä (01/01/2021) kuuluu 12/31/2020 "
"selvitykseen, joten **avaava** selvitys on 12/31/2020."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:106
msgid "Once the data is in the :guilabel:`Report 1 Download` sheet:"
msgstr "Kun tiedot ovat :guilabel:`Report 1 Download` -välilehdellä:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:108
msgid "Go to the :guilabel:`Transaction Search` tab on Authorize.Net."
msgstr ""
"Siirry :guilabel:`Transaction Search` -välilehdelle Authorize.Net-"
"järjestelmässä."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:109
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Settlement Date` section, select the previously used "
"range of batch settlement dates in the :guilabel:`From:` and :guilabel:`To:` "
"fields and click :guilabel:`Search`."
msgstr ""
"Valitse :guilabel:`Settlement Date` -osiossa aiemmin käytetty "
"eräselvityspäivämäärien alue :guilabel:`From:`- ja :guilabel:`To:` -kenttiin "
"ja napsauta :guilabel:`Search`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:111
msgid "When the list has been generated, click :guilabel:`Download to File`."
msgstr "Kun luettelo on muodostettu, napsauta :guilabel:`Download to File`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:112
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, select :guilabel:`Expanded Fields with CAVV Response/"
"Comma Separated`, enable :guilabel:`Include Column Headings`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Submit`."
msgstr ""
"Valitse ponnahdusikkunassa :guilabel:`Expanded Fields with CAVV Response/"
"Comma Separated`, ota käyttöön :guilabel:`Include Column Headings` ja "
"napsauta :guilabel:`Submit`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:114
msgid ""
"Open the text file, select :guilabel:`All`, copy the data, and paste it into "
"the :guilabel:`Report 2 Download` sheet of the :ref:`Excel import template "
"<authorize-import-template>`."
msgstr ""
"Avaa tekstitiedosto, valitse :guilabel:`All`, kopioi tiedot ja liitä "
"ne :guilabel:`Report 2 Download` -välilehteen :ref:`Excel-tuontipohjassa "
"<authorize-import-template>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:116
msgid ""
"Transit lines are automatically filled in and updated in "
"the :guilabel:`transit for report 1` and :guilabel:`transit for report 2` "
"sheets of the :ref:`Excel import template <authorize-import-template>`. Make "
"sure all entries are present, and **if not**, copy the formula from "
"previously filled-in lines of the :guilabel:`transit for report 1` "
"or :guilabel:`2` sheets and paste it into the empty lines."
msgstr ""
"Siirtorivit täytetään ja päivitetään automaattisesti :guilabel:`transit for "
"report 1`- ja :guilabel:`transit for report 2` -välilehdille :ref:`Excel-"
"tuontipohjassa <authorize-import-template>`. Varmista, että kaikki merkinnät "
"ovat läsnä, ja **jos eivät**, kopioi kaava aiemmin täytetyiltä "
"riveiltä :guilabel:`transit for report 1`- tai :guilabel:`2` -välilehdillä "
"ja liitä se tyhjille riveille."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:123
msgid ""
"To get the correct closing balance, **do not remove** any line from the "
"Excel sheets."
msgstr ""
"Saadaksesi oikean loppusaldon, **älä poista** yhtään riviä Excel-"
"välilehdiltä."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:126
msgid "Import into Odoo"
msgstr "Tuonti Odoohon"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:128
msgid "To import the data into Odoo:"
msgstr "Tietojen tuominen Odoohon:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:130
msgid "Open the :ref:`Excel import template <authorize-import-template>`."
msgstr "Avaa :ref:`Excel-tuontipohja <authorize-import-template>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:131
msgid ""
"Copy the data from the :guilabel:`transit for report 2` sheet and use *paste "
"special* to only paste the values in the :guilabel:`Odoo Import to CSV` "
"sheet."
msgstr ""
"Kopioi tiedot :guilabel:`transit for report 2` -välilehdeltä ja käytä *liitä "
"määräten* -toimintoa liittääksesi vain arvot :guilabel:`Odoo Import to CSV` "
"-välilehdelle."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:133
msgid ""
"Look for *blue* cells in the :guilabel:`Odoo Import to CSV` sheet. These are "
"chargeback entries without any reference number. As they cannot be imported "
"as such, go to :menuselection:`Authorize.Net --> Account --> Statements --> "
"eCheck.Net Settlement Statement`."
msgstr ""
"Etsi *siniset* solut :guilabel:`Odoo Import to CSV` -välilehdeltä. Nämä ovat "
"takaisinveloitusmerkintöjä ilman viitenumeroa. Koska niitä ei voi tuoda "
"sellaisinaan, siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`Authorize.Net --> Account --> "
"Statements --> eCheck.Net Settlement Statement`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:136
msgid "Look for :guilabel:`Charge Transaction/Chargeback`, and click it."
msgstr "Etsi :guilabel:`Charge Transaction/Chargeback` ja napsauta sitä."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:137
msgid ""
"Copy the invoice description, paste it into the :guilabel:`Label` cell of "
"the :guilabel:`Odoo Import to CSV` sheet, and add `Chargeback /` before the "
"description."
msgstr ""
"Kopioi laskun kuvaus, liitä se :guilabel:`Label` -soluun :guilabel:`Odoo "
"Import to CSV` -välilehdellä ja lisää `Chargeback /` ennen kuvausta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:139
msgid ""
"If there are multiple invoices, add a line into the :ref:`Excel import "
"template <authorize-import-template>` for each invoice and copy/paste the "
"description into each respective :guilabel:`Label` line."
msgstr ""
"Jos laskuja on useita, lisää rivi :ref:`Excel-tuontipohjaan <authorize-"
"import-template>` kutakin laskua varten ja kopioi/liitä kuvaus "
"jokaiselle :guilabel:`Label` -riville."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:144
msgid ""
"For **combined chargeback/returns** in the payouts, create a new line in "
"the :ref:`Excel import template <authorize-import-template>` for each "
"invoice."
msgstr ""
"Käsittele **yhdistetyt takaisinveloitukset/palautukset** maksuissa luomalla "
"uusi rivi :ref:`Excel-tuontipohjaan <authorize-import-template>` kutakin "
"laskua varten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:0
msgid "Chargeback description"
msgstr "Takaisinveloituksen kuvaus"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:152
msgid ""
"Next, delete *zero transaction* and *void transaction* line items, and "
"change the format of the :guilabel:`Amount` column in the :guilabel:`Odoo "
"Import to CSV` sheet to *Number*."
msgstr ""
"Poista seuraavaksi *nollatransaktio*- ja *mitätöity transaktio* -rivit ja "
"muuta :guilabel:`Amount` -sarakkeen muoto :guilabel:`Odoo Import to CSV` "
"-välilehdellä muotoon *Number*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:154
msgid ""
"Go back to :menuselection:`eCheck.Net Settlement Statement --> Search for a "
"Transaction` and search again for the previously used batch settlements "
"dates."
msgstr ""
"Palaa kohtaan :menuselection:`eCheck.Net Settlement Statement --> Search for "
"a Transaction` ja hae uudelleen aiemmin käytettyjä erätilityksen päivämääriä."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:156
msgid ""
"Verify that the batch settlement dates on eCheck.Net match the related "
"payments' dates found in the :guilabel:`Date` column of the :guilabel:`Odoo "
"Import to CSV`."
msgstr ""
"Tarkista, että erätilityksen päivämäärät eCheck.Net-palvelussa vastaavat "
"liittyvien maksujen päivämääriä, jotka löytyvät :guilabel:`Date` "
"-sarakkeesta :guilabel:`Odoo Import to CSV` -välilehdellä."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:158
msgid ""
"If it does not match, replace the date with the one from eCheck.Net. Sort "
"the column by *date*, and make sure the format is `MM/DD/YYYY`."
msgstr ""
"Jos ne eivät täsmää, korvaa päivämäärä eCheck.Net-palvelusta löytyvällä "
"päivämäärällä. Lajittele sarake *päivämäärän* mukaan ja varmista, että muoto "
"on `MM/DD/YYYY`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:160
msgid ""
"Copy the data - column headings included - from the :guilabel:`Odoo Import "
"to CSV` sheet, paste it into a new Excel file, and save it using the CSV "
"format."
msgstr ""
"Kopioi tiedot - sarakkeen otsikot mukaan lukien - :guilabel:`Odoo Import to "
"CSV` -välilehdeltä, liitä ne uuteen Excel-tiedostoon ja tallenna se CSV-"
"muodossa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:162
msgid ""
"Open the Accounting app, go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Journals`, "
"tick the :guilabel:`Authorize.Net` box, and click :menuselection:`Favorites "
"--> Import records --> Load file`. Select the CSV file and upload it into "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Avaa Kirjanpito-sovellus, siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`Configuration --> "
"Journals`, valitse :guilabel:`Authorize.Net` -valintaruutu ja "
"napsauta :menuselection:`Favorites --> Import records --> Load file`. "
"Valitse CSV-tiedosto ja lataa se Odoohon."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:167
msgid ""
"List of `eCheck.Net return codes <https://support.authorize.net/"
"knowledgebase/Knowledgearticle/?code=000001293>`_"
msgstr ""
"Luettelo `eCheck.Net-palautuskoodeista <https://support.authorize.net/"
"knowledgebase/Knowledgearticle/?code=000001293>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:3
msgid "Buckaroo"
msgstr "Buckaroo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Buckaroo <https://www.buckaroo.eu/>`_ is a Dutch-based company that offers "
"several online payment possibilities."
msgstr ""
"<https://www.buckaroo.eu/>`_ on Hollannissa toimiva yritys, joka tarjoaa "
"useita verkkomaksuvaihtoehtoja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:11
msgid "Configuration on Buckaroo Plaza"
msgstr "Määritykset Buckaroo Plazassa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:13
msgid ""
"Log into `Buckaroo Plaza <https://plaza.buckaroo.nl>`_, go "
"to :menuselection:`My Buckaroo --> Websites` and select the :guilabel:`Push "
"settings` tab."
msgstr ""
"Kirjaudu sisään `Buckaroo Plaza <https://plaza.buckaroo.nl>`_ -palveluun, "
"siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`My Buckaroo --> Websites` ja "
"valitse :guilabel:`Push settings` -välilehti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:15
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Enable Push Response` check box in "
"the :guilabel:`Delayed and Push responses` section."
msgstr ""
"Valitse :guilabel:`Enable Push Response` -valintaruutu :guilabel:`Delayed "
"and Push responses` -osiossa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:17
msgid ""
"Enter the URL of your Odoo database, followed by `/payment/buckaroo/webhook` "
"in both the :guilabel:`Push URI Success/Pending` and :guilabel:`Push URI "
"Failure` text fields. For example: `https://yourcompany.odoo.com/payment/"
"buckaroo/webhook`."
msgstr ""
"Syötä Odoo-tietokantasi URL-osoite, jota seuraa `/payment/buckaroo/webhook` "
"sekä :guilabel:`Push URI Success/Pending` että :guilabel:`Push URI Failure` "
"-tekstikenttiin. Esimerkiksi: `https://yourcompany.odoo.com/payment/buckaroo/"
"webhook`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:20
msgid "Leave the other fields as they are and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Jätä muut kentät ennalleen ja napsauta :guilabel:`Tallenna`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:21
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`General` tab, copy the website :guilabel:`Key` (i.e., the "
"key used to uniquely identify your website with Buckaroo) and save it for "
"later."
msgstr ""
"Kopioi :guilabel:`Yleiset` -välilehdeltä verkkosivun :guilabel:`Avain` (eli "
"avain, jolla verkkosivu yksiselitteisesti tunnistetaan Buckaroon kanssa) ja "
"tallenna se myöhempää käyttöä varten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:23
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Security --> Secret key`, enter "
"or :guilabel:`Generate` a :guilabel:`Secret key` and click :guilabel:`Save`. "
"Save the key for later."
msgstr ""
"Siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`Asetukset --> Tietoturva --> Salainen avain`, "
"syötä tai :guilabel:`Luo` :guilabel:`Salainen avain` ja "
"napsauta :guilabel:`Tallenna`. Tallenna avain myöhempää käyttöä varten."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:29
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the payment provider Buckaroo <payment_providers/add_new>` "
"and change its state to :guilabel:`Enabled`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Siirry maksuntarjoajaan Buckaroo <payment_providers/add_new>` ja "
"vaihda sen tilaksi :guilabel:`Käytössä`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:31
